Well, today we headed off on the return trip to Sioux Falls. It was an
interesting mix of a ride: some really great roads (one of which
will be getting its own dedicated post at a later date), some
mind-numbing & sleep-inducing stretches, 100+ F temperatures, and a shorter
ride than we have been doing, yet also more grueling in a completely mundane
sort of way.

