## Cody to Thermopolis

The stretch from Cody to Thermopolis was one of the low points of the day, with
two notable exceptions: the rest area before Greybull which also happened to host
"The Museum of Flight And Aerial Firefighters" was a life saver. I was feeling
pretty drowsy before we got here and needed to shake off the boredom.

